                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7502" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0196</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2195 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">加冠种松桂，早晚见成林：乘木科技数字时代的责任与担当</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate Social Responsibility of Syncsmart in the Digital Age</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汪玥琦，胡辰光（通讯作者），王鹏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乘木科技（珠海）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；利益相关者；数字经济；数字孪生；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate social responsibility, stakeholder, digital economy, digital twin</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新一轮科技革命和产业变革正在深刻改变世界发展的面貌和格局，科学新发现、技术新突破在造福人类的同时，也带来了伦理风险和挑战。因此，科技向善解决社会痛点、情怀担当促进社会进步成为了全社会的期望。本案例聚焦乘木科技（珠海）有限公司，一家专注于应用数字孪生技术助力智慧城市建设的科技型企业，以公司创始人的创业历程为主线，描述了公司如何将国家需求、社会期望同公司业务重心与发展战略有机结合，乘着数字经济、智慧城市建设的时代东风，通过逐步拓展应用场景、助力科技成果转化、回馈生态共同体等举措，实现公司成长的过程。本案例重点探讨企业应对谁负责、负责什么、为何负责、如何负责等问题，旨在引导学生掌握利益相关者视角、数字时代的三重底线模型等知识点，并把握数字企业社会责任履行的实施过程、实践范式等要点，提升学生理论联系实际、分析并解决实际问题的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Technological reform and industrial revolution have profoundly altered the pattern of world development. Scientific discoveries and technological breakthroughs not only benefit mankind, but also present ethical risks and challenges. It thus becomes a common expectation of society to address societal sore points and catalyze societal progress with the help of technologies for social goods. This case focuses on Syncsmart (Zhuhai) Co., Ltd., a technological venture which concentrates on applying digital twin technology to build smart cities. Following the entrepreneurial journey of the company founders, this case describes how Syncsmart integrates the state demand and social expectations with the company’s business and development strategy. Specifically, the case introduces the company’s growing process, under the wave of digital technology and smart city, in extending application scenarios, commercializing research findings, and contributing to the ecological community. Through discussing for whom, what, why, and how Syncsmart should be socially responsible, the case aims to guide students to grasp the stakeholder perspective, the triple-bottom-line model in the digital age, the implementation process and the paradigm of corporate social responsibility of digital firms. By doing so, the case aims to enhance students’ capability to connect theories with practice and address issues in corporate social responsibility.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者；数字时代的三重底线模型；企业社会责任的驱动因素；数字企业社会责任履行的实施程序与实践范式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
